passages.text:
Khan: Hey, Logar.
[[(Logar_Reply_FriendlyKhan)]]
[[(Logar_Reply_HostileKhan)]]
passages.name: (Begin)

passages.text:
Logar: Oh Khan, you're here at a good time. I have a request.
[[(Khan_LogarFriendlyReply)]]
Sequence:
None()
Conditions:
Variable["Story_Timeline"] == 2 and
Variable["Story_RiceAndFish_Logar_ConvincedHelp"] == true and 
Variable["Story_RiceAndFish_Mutt_SpyForMutt"] == false
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_FriendlyKhan)

passages.text:
Logar: Why are you here as well, Logar ? What with you people ? Don't you have things to do ?

[[(Khan_LogarHostile)]]

Sequence:
None()
Conditions:
Variable["Story_Timeline"] == 2 and
Variable["Story_RiceAndFish_Logar_ConvincedHelp"] == false and 
Variable["Story_RiceAndFish_Mutt_SpyForMutt"] == false
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_HostileKhan)

passages.text:
Khan: Huh? What did you just say ?.
[[(Logar_Reply2)]]
passages.name: (Khan_LogarFriendlyReply)

passages.text:
Logar: I said that I have a request. Are you dull ?
[[(Khan_Reply2)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply2)

passages.text:
Khan: Of.. Of course, since you're behavior are some what inconsistent...
[[(Logar_Reyply3)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Reply2)

passages.text:
Logar: I wouldn't have done it but since our friend here convinced me otherwise.
[[(Logar_Reply3_1)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reyply3)

passages.text:
Logar: Then Khan, I will need a new hook. If you can make that for me I'll do you a favor.
[[(Khan_Reply_3)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply3_1)

passages.text:
Khan: Ah I knew our mind are compatible my friend.
[[(Logar_Reply_4)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Reply_3)

passages.text:
Logar: No we're not, don't push it. So what do you want ?
[[(Khan_Reply_4)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_4)

passages.text:
Khan: .... , so do you have a soft spot afterall.
[[(Logar_Reply_5)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Reply_4)

passages.text:
Logar: I said... DON'T PUSH IT.
[[(Khan_Reply_5)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_5)

passages.text:
Khan:... Okay then, I will need your fish. A lot of them.
[[(Logar_Reply_6)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Reply_5)

passages.text:
Logar: Fine, do my things and you can have them. 
[[(Khan_Reply_6)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_6)

passages.text:
Khan: Your not going to ask why ?
[[(Logar_Reply_7)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Reply_6)

passages.text:
Khan: Do I look like I care ?.
[[(Logar_Reply_8)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_7)

passages.text:
Logar: I see.... well It is settled then. 
[[(END)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Reply_8)

passages.text:
Sequence:
None()
passages.name: (END)

passages.text:
Khan: Oh I'm here to ask for your aid.

[[(Logar_Hostile_1)]]
passages.name: (Khan_LogarHostile)

passages.text:
Logar: .... I'm going back inside, don't follow me.
[[(Khan_Hostile_1)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Hostile_1)

passages.text:

(set: $Story_RiceAndFish_Logar_KnowsAboutMutt = true)
Logar: He said WHAT ?
[[(Logar_Knows_1)]]
Conditions:
Variable["Story_RiceAndFish_Mutt_SpyForMutt"] == true
passages.name: Player:TellLogarAboutMutt

passages.text:
Logar: That scheming UNRA, you know what Khan, if you kick Mutt out and make me a new hook. I give you all the fish you want.

[[(Khan_Knows_1)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Knows_1)

passages.text:
Khan: Really ?, but Mutt is a friend too. 
[[(Logar_Knows_2)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Knows_1)

passages.text:
Logar: What kind of friend does that ?... Do you want my help or not ? You came here for a reason right ?
[[(Khan_Knows_2)]]
passages.name: (Logar_Knows_2)

passages.text:
Khan: Yes, .....
[[(Khan_Knows_2_1)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Knows_2)

passages.text:
Khan: After  making you the hook and kick Mutt out. I will need another thing.
[[(Logar_Knows_3)]]
passages.name: (Khan_Knows_2_1)

passages.text:
Logar: What ? Spill it out!

[[(Khan_Reply_5)]]
